channel.title: Error connecting to server =\
channel.description:
Hey everyone,
I've been having trouble connecting to a server that i just downloaded, i get no error messages, and i went in gui and switched the server ip, is there anything else i gotta do?
By the way, I am using deathzscape and deathzscape client v2

item.title: Error connecting to server =\
item.dc:creator: @new2servers new2servers
item.description:
@new2servers wrote:

ok i went to http://www.canyouseeme.org/ and got Success: I can see your service on (my ip adress) on port (43594)
Your ISP is not blocking port 43594

and then i went onto my router, made sure my server was enabled (the little check box) it is

then went to duct setup thing and that was enabled too
